  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The homeopathic remedy 'naja-comp' will improve functional outcome measured by the
      Barthel-Index.

      The homeopathic remedy 'naja-comp' will decrease complications during geriatric
      rehabilitation measured by rate of unplanned discharge to hospital.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Secondary outcome for functional improvement are Scandinavian Stroke Scale, 4D+S-Scale and
      Timed-Up&amp;Go-Test.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
